Program & Dependency Install
----------------------------
Terminal: [xfce4-terminal, zsh, chsh, Oh-My-ZSH]
- No longer using Kitty, I use xfce4-terminal for transparent background
- Shell is ZSH w/ Oh-My-ZSH and 'awesome panda' theming  

WM: [i3, dmenu, feh, polybar]
- Modifier changed to ALT
- Changed default terminal launch
- Support for polybar  

IDE: [neovim]
- Pulls from .vimrc
- Theme (Fluctuates, currently Dracula)
- Vim-plug plugin manager
- fzf Fuzzy Finder
- NERDTree Explorer
- Treesitter
- Airline  

Browser: [microsoft-edge-stable[
 - Apps:
    - Reddit
    - Twitter
    - YouTube
    - Twitch
- Linked to Microsoft Account for everything else

